div.p:
A visit along these lines could include: 

— a ceremonial visit to the Rathaus and signature of the Golden
                            Book;

— a stop at a Berlin institution; industrial, cultural or
                            governmental;

— an act taking cognizance of the division of the city, such as a
                            visit to the Wall;

— some contact with Allied forces such as a visit to American
                            Headquarters or one of the main barracks complexes.
